@endpoint POST /
@desc Creates a temporary URL to start an AppStream 2.0 streaming session for the specified user. A streaming URL enables application streaming to be tested without user setup.
@required {StackName: str, FleetName: str, UserId: str}
@optional {ApplicationId: str, Validity: int(i64), SessionContext: str}
@returns(200) {StreamingURL: str?, Expires: str(timestamp)?}

