@returns(200) {Fleets: [Fleet]?, NextToken: str?}

@endpoint POST /
@desc Retrieves a list that describes one or more specified image builders, if the image builder names are provided. Otherwise, all image builders in the account are described.
@optional {Names: [str], MaxResults: int, NextToken: str}
@returns(200) {ImageBuilders: [ImageBuilder]?, NextToken: str?}

